Best Pracs
-referential integrity
-migration workflows with db push
-indices on foreign keys


-accounts
  id
  mud_id (from the mud)
  created_date
  modified_date
  first_name
  last_name
  email

-network_history
  id
  account_id      -> accounts.id
  ip_address
  last_login_date
  last_failed_login_date

-network_blacklist
  id
  network_history_id      -> network_history.id
  issue_date
  term_date
  issuer                  -> accounts.id

-account_roles
  id
  account_id    -> accounts.id
  role_id
  issue_date
  issuer_id     -> accounts.id

-roles
  id
  type

-account_passwords
  id
  account_hash
  password_hash

-account_preferences
  id
  receive_notifications     -> notification enums[]
  default_theme
  show_side_panel

-account_notifications
  id
  account_id        -> accounts.id
  notification_id   -> notifications.id
  read
  read_date

